<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ding un! Ding un, Isu di'n!
 Nanghaw Kross sepaihte;
 A Lal puonlap dawmsang un,
 Mang ngeilo ding ahi;
 Galzo a, zo zel dingin,
 A sepaih puihuoi ding;
 Melma nuoisieh ahih a,
 Krista leng A chan nan.

[V2]
 2. Ding un! Ding un, Isu di'n,
 Pengkun sapna ngaiun;
 Kidona phuolah pang un,
 A ni lopi a hin;
 Nanghaw, Amah nasemte'n,
 Gal simsen loh do in;
 Lauhum na-ah hangsan un,
 Hat takin do zel un.

[V3]
 3. Ding un! Ding un! Isu di'n!
 Amah hatna muong un;
 Na sapum ban thahatnau,
 Senin do zo puon lau;
 Gospel galvan chu lauin,
 Paucham un la, do un;
 Lauh umna na tuok tieng leh,
 Chau in puk ngei puon lau.

[V4]
 4. Ding un! Ding un! Isu di'n!
 Kido sawtta puona;
 Tuhin kido thawm I zai,
 Dan leh galzawhna la
 Kuole guolzo te cheng chun,
 Hinna lukhuk chang ding;
 Lopina Lalpen chu tawh,
 Kumsawta vaihawm ding.</lyrics>
<title>STAND UP FOR JESUS</title>
<hymn_number>303</hymn_number>
</song>